Install Brew:
/usr/bin/ruby -e "$(curl -fsSL https://raw.githubusercontent.com/Homebrew/install/master/install)"

Install Mongo db by brew:
- brew update
- brew install mongodb

If mac version error
- brew search mongodb
- brew install mongodb@3.4

Manual Install:
- Download the tarball for your system from the MongoDB Download Center
  (https://www.mongodb.com/download-center?&_ga=2.80712343.1634145276.1533123316-981468549.1532670233#production)
- Go to folder /usr/local/bin
- Copy all the downloaded bin files.
- In terminal enter mongod.

Project Installation:
- npm install mongodb --save
- mongod --dpath /databasepath
